name: home_activity
text:
You’re doing great towards your goal, {{1}}. Were you able to {{2}}?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. Yes
2. Not yet

name: first_module_intro
text:
It’s time to get started on your goal, {{1}}. Are you ready?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. Yes!
2. Remind me tomorrow

name: start_started_mod_or_change_goal
text:
You're almost finished with this goal! {{1}} What would you like to do?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. {{2}}
2. Leave this goal unfinished and select a new goal

name: unfinished_onboarding
text:
ParentText has begun. Are you ready to complete your registration and select your parenting goals?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. Yes
2. Remind me Later

name: select_goal
text:
You have made great progress. Are you ready to select your next parenting goal?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. Yes
2. Remind me Later

name: no_response
text: These messages don’t seem to be working. When you are ready to keep going, press 1.

name: post_goal_checkin
text: Today we are taking a break from your goal, {{1}}, and checking in on your progress. Press 1 on your keypad to proceed.

name: complete_start_module
text:
You’re off track! Do you want to complete a previous skill or start a new skill?

Press a number on your keypad:
1. Complete
2. Start new
